CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_6: When you have installed the app, check that the app its running and you're logged.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_7: A new virtual drive will appear on your filesystem (D: E: F: whatever)
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_8: Now, inside the virtual drive, create a new folder, call it 'servihelper' for example. If you are the first one to sync the files then prepare the link to share this new folder.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_9: (When the other admins install the same app, they need to use you link and the folder will appear on their filesystem with all the data)
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_10: Then, lets notify servihelper about this shared folder.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_11: Click on the next slider button and an input field to paste the system shared folder path will appear.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_12: The route to the shared folder changes from Windows, Mac or Linux. In Windows should be something like: G:\My Space\servihelper (letter can change)
PLACEHOLDER_SHARED_FOLDER_LABEL: Enter the system shared folder path
CONFIG_ONLINE_FOLDER_ERROR: The provided system url is not valid
CONFIG_ASK_MOVE_FILES: Do you want to move the current offline files to the shared folder?
CONFIG_YES_WARNING: Be careful! Click {{BUTTON_YES}} only if you are the first one to synchronize the files.
CONFIG_CANNOT_COPY: Cannot copy servihelper files to shared folder, some file already exists
CONFIG_DEFAULT_FONT_SIZE_VERTICAL: Vertical reports default font size in pixels (doesn't affect pdf)
CONFIG_DEFAULT_FONT_SIZE_HORIZONTAL: Horizontal reports default font size in pixels (doesn't affect pdf)
CONFIG_DEFAULT_FONT_SIZE_HORIZONTAL_TIP: Font size must be smaller to fit all the a4 page
APP_ONLINE_TIMEOUT_REMINDER: When working online the app will close after 15 minuts 🕒 if there is no activity.
RESTART_APP: The new configuration requires Servihelper to be closed and opened again.
HOME_IS_ONLINE_ACTIVATED: ⚠️ Online mode is activated. Please make sure you have the latest files from the shared folder. If not, close servihelper and get them first.
ICON_PDF_BAND: Generate a colorful pdf specially for the midweek with bands and up to two weeks per page
ICON_PDF_BAND_WEEKEND: Generate a colorful pdf specially for the weekend with bands and up to five weeks per page
